concepts.NEW_SIGN/SYMPTOM_33_DESC: Whether the patient's sign or symptom was newly described (during this encounter)
concepts.CURRENTLY_TAKING_MEDICATION_15_DESC: Question as part of medication history
concepts.HISTORICAL_DRUG_START_DATE_49_DESC: Information gathered on encounter forms which describes the date of a particular drug's institution.  Most often "globbed" with another concept which describes the drug.
concepts.PREGNANCY_STATUS_18_DESC: Question on encounter form: "Is the patient pregnant?"
concepts.DATE_OF_TEST_RESULT_17_DESC: Date/time that a test result was obtained. This is not when the test was ordered, or when the result was given to the patient.
